      "description": "The Tuttle Capital Bitcoin 0DTE Covered Call ETF (BITK) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in long btc, short usd currency. The fund seeks current income via a synthetic covered call strategy on Bitcoin through the iShares Bitcoin Trust ETF (NASDAQ: IBIT). The fund will sell call options with zero days to expiration (0DTE) options. BITK was launched on Sep 24, 2025 and is issued by Tuttle Capital.",
